DESCRIPTION:Weekly Digital Call Agenda:&nbsp\;<br><ul><li>Analytics\, highl
 ights and interpretations from the week</li><li>Successes to repeat\, place
 s to improve&nbsp\;</li><li>Current climate: what is happening\, what shoul
 d we be tapping into in the week ahead?</li><li>Upcoming content and recomm
 endations for cadence&nbsp\;</li><li>Questions\, concerns\, shares...</li><
 /ul><br><u>For the Aug 5th Call:&nbsp\;</u><br><br>We have a lot of change 
 within our digital teams. Welcome Sara\, from NILC and Jacqueline from Soze
 !&nbsp\;<br>I'd like to go over ASANA and workflow today to onboard those w
 ho are new\, and I think the rest of us could use a refresh.&nbsp\;<br><br>
 Talk soon!&nbsp\;\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:
 ~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-\nJoin with Google Meet: https://meet.goog
