DESCRIPTION:Hi advocates\,<br><br>Welcome to our joint LegList/Amigos calls
  every Tuesday from 12pm-1pm ET.<br><br>Sharing below the *<b>Zoom link</b>
 * for this call. This is a brand new link specific to these calls. <br><br>
 <b>Join Zoom Meeting<br></b><a href="https://theimmigrationhub.zoom.us/j/99
 688610073?pwd=WKn0u5kMPcEPmhRhOFWpNvjfzpaBxJ.1">https://theimmigrationhub.z
 oom.us/j/99688610073?pwd=WKn0u5kMPcEPmhRhOFWpNvjfzpaBxJ.1</a><br><br>Meetin
 g ID: 996 8861 0073<br>Password: 466885<br><br><br>Agenda items are always 
 welcome.<b> Please send <a href="mailto:joshua@theimmigrationhub.org" targe
 t="_blank">joshua@theimmigrationhub.org</a> any agenda items by COB on Frid
 ays.</b><br><b><br>Guidelines for the Amigos Listserv &amp\; Calls</b><br>T
 he Amigos network is a collaborative space created to facilitate informatio
 n-sharing and activation of partners on timely immigration issues. We great
 ly value our partners in the Amigos network and seek to foster a culture of
  trust\, equity\, and community. With this in mind\, we have implemented th
 e guidelines outlined below to inform how we show up for ourselves and for 
 each other. <br><br><b>The full version of the Amigos list guidelines can b
 e found here: </b><a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1poTzhnjlpqJz
 dJ65VMkC9Lo091h08Ojj2fpYgkRN9-4/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank"><u><u><u>
 https://docs.google.com/document/d/1poTzhnjlpqJzdJ65VMkC9Lo091h08Ojj2fpYgkR
 N9-4/edit?usp=sharing</u></u></u></a><br><br>Failure to abide by these guid
 elines may result in removal from the Hub’s Amigos listserv and may also ex
 tend to other Hub listservs\, such as Leglist and Admin List/Table. Removal
  from the Amigos calls/listserv can be made at the discretion of Immigratio
 n Hub staff and may be done immediately\, without warning\, based on the of
 fending action(s). <br><br><b>The Amigos Network</b><br>The purpose of both
  the Amigos listserv and weekly Amigos calls is for organizations to share 
 updates\, resources\, and actions on federal immigration and refugee policy
  issues\; coordinate advocacy on federal legislation and executive policy\;
  and rapidly respond to national immigration and refugee policy development
 s.<br><br>At this time\, approximately 100 partners consistently join the w
 eekly Amigos calls. A regularly-updated list of Amigos partners can be view
 ed here: <br><br><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Q0A_LyzM_
 IYF9zV7WxwfICJOC53yBOj7LcHjVM8vNqA/edit#gid=0" target="_blank"><u><u><u>htt
 ps://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Q0A_LyzM_IYF9zV7WxwfICJOC53yBOj7LcHjVM
 8vNqA/edit#gid=0</u></u></u></a><br><br>If you have any questions about the
  network\, or would like to add people to the listserv\, please email: <a h
 ref="mailto:joshua@theimmigrationhub.org" target="_blank">joshua@theimmigra
 tionhub.org</a><br><b><u><br></u></b>Best\,<br><br>Josh\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:
 ~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-\nJo
 in Zoom Meeting\nhttps://theimmigrationhub.zoom.us/j/99688610073 (ID: 99688
 610073\, passcode: 466885)\n\nJoin by phone\n(US) +1 346-248-7799 (passcode
 : 466885)\n\nJoining instructions: https://www.google.com/url?q=https://app
 lications.zoom.us/addon/invitation/detail?meetingUuid%3DpEd5DF2iSzqfhEJrGbI
 vfw%253D%253D%26signature%3Dcc96fa56b476fee949dbfee536391d7ad43355aa90f1645
 1f1a0d72e83da4103%26v%3D1&sa=D&source=calendar&usg=AOvVaw2T24fArq-E-AAcdQH5
 -M2k\n\nMeeting host: <a href="mailto:joshua@theimmigrationhub.org" target=
 "_blank">joshua@theimmigrationhub.org</a><br /><br />Join Zoom Meeting: <br
  /><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://theimmigrationhub.zoom.us/
 j/99688610073&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;usg=AOvVaw0yVrv5uEPzTreOH
 cNglRxE" target="_blank">https://theimmigrationhub.zoom.us/j/99688610073</a
