 o are users of the site. I recognize there are some setting changes that wi
 ll need to be made\, and we want to preserve our NILC security while also e
 nsuring we can move forward with this important internal communication func
 tion.</p><p>James+Steven\, please work together to make this happen\, and l
 et me and Jasmin know if there’s anything you need in the process. Jasmin h
 as set up a Test list to send the emails\, which we want to use before we r
 oll out the function and start emailing all staff.</p><p>Please keep me pos
 ted\, and I’ll reach back out in a week for a status report if I haven’t he
 ard from you.</p>\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:
