DESCRIPTION:Event Name: 60 Minute Meeting\n\nBuckle up. Let's Go!\n\nLocati
 on: This is a Google Meet web conference.\nYou can join this meeting from y
 our computer\, tablet\, or smartphone.\nhttps://calendly.com/events/52e843a
 3-92a9-428b-879b-36b97b65f2a6/google_meet\n\nPlease share anything that wil
 l help prepare for our meeting.:\nHi Kevin\,\n\nWe’re ready to move forward
  with setting up a merch shop. Before we do\, we have a few clarifying ques
 tions:\n\n* Is it possible to launch with four items instead of three? If w
 e have three items in our shop\, is it possible to offer a fourth\, and dif
 ferent item\, to our email list?\n*Based on your experience\, what are your
  top-selling merchandise items? Are there specific items you recommend nonp
 rofits start with?\n*During our previous call\, we mentioned the idea of of
 fering a printed poster. Could you share what the cost would be to include 
 a poster in the shop?\n*Does Worx offer a yard sign —something like this?\n
 *For the full-color sticker pack\, do we need to provide three different st
 icker designs?\n*Do you have resources to ensure our designs are properly f
 ormatted for the products and include the necessary dimensions for correct 
 export?\n*At checkout\, are customers prompted to add a donation? If not\, 
 would it be possible to include a feature like “Would you like to add a don
 ation?”\n*Could you also share more about how nonprofits have used the stor
 e to steward donors or engage their email lists? For example\, do they typi
 cally send merch to specific donor segments—like monthly donors—or offer ex
 clusive items as a thank-you? Do nonprofits usually pay upfront for the mer
 ch\, or is it more common to offer an exclusive item as a benefit for being
  on the email list?\n\nWe thought it might be easier to discuss all of this
  in a conversation.\nJasmin\n\nNeed to make changes to this event?\nCancel:
  https://calendly.com/cancellations/266bea4e-06b9-4d3c-9a07-e88746961b25\nR
 eschedule: https://calendly.com/reschedulings/266bea4e-06b9-4d3c-9a07-e8874
 6961b25\n\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:
 ~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-\nJoin with Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/j
 up-nzdk-mps\nOr dial: (US) +1 218-460-1368 PIN: 345557024#\nMore phone numb
 ers: https://tel.meet/jup-nzdk-mps?pin=2442821082150&hs=7\n\nLearn more abo
 ut Meet at: https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720\n\nPlease do 
 not edit this section.\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-
