DESCRIPTION:Hi advocates\,<br><br>Welcome to our joint LegList/Amigos calls
  every Tuesday from 12pm-1pm ET.<br><br>Sharing below the *<b>Zoom link</b>
 * for this call. This is a brand new link specific to these calls. <br><br>
 <b>Join Zoom Meeting</b><br><a href="https://theimmigrationhub.zoom.us/j/93
 071803953?pwd=f6bIsNBmpodar3JOMyp72BLXecG0bb.1">https://theimmigrationhub.z
 oom.us/j/93071803953?pwd=f6bIsNBmpodar3JOMyp72BLXecG0bb.1</a><br><br>Meetin
 g ID: 930 7180 3953<br>Password: 124414<br><br>Agenda items are always welc
 ome.<b> Please send <a href="mailto:joshua@theimmigrationhub.org" target="_
 blank"><u>joshua@theimmigrationhub.org</u></a> any agenda items by COB on F
 ridays.</b><br><b><br>Guidelines for the Amigos Listserv &amp\; Calls</b><b
 r>The Amigos network is a collaborative space created to facilitate informa
 tion-sharing and activation of partners on timely immigration issues. We gr
 eatly value our partners in the Amigos network and seek to foster a culture
  of trust\, equity\, and community. With this in mind\, we have implemented
  the guidelines outlined below to inform how we show up for ourselves and f
 or each other. <br><br><b>The full version of the Amigos list guidelines ca
 n be found here: </b><a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1poTzhnjlp
 qJzdJ65VMkC9Lo091h08Ojj2fpYgkRN9-4/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank"><u><u>
 <u><u>https://docs.google.com/document/d/1poTzhnjlpqJzdJ65VMkC9Lo091h08Ojj2
 fpYgkRN9-4/edit?usp=sharing</u></u></u></u></a><br><br>Failure to abide by 
 these guidelines may result in removal from the Hub’s Amigos listserv and m
 ay also extend to other Hub listservs\, such as Leglist and Admin List/Tabl
 e. Removal from the Amigos calls/listserv can be made at the discretion of 
 Immigration Hub staff and may be done immediately\, without warning\, based
  on the offending action(s). <br><br><b>The Amigos Network</b><br>The purpo
 se of both the Amigos listserv and weekly Amigos calls is for organizations
  to share updates\, resources\, and actions on federal immigration and refu
 gee policy issues\; coordinate advocacy on federal legislation and executiv
 e policy\; and rapidly respond to national immigration and refugee policy d
 evelopments.<br><br>At this time\, approximately 100 partners consistently 
 join the weekly Amigos calls. A regularly-updated list of Amigos partners c
 an be viewed here: <br><br><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/
 1Q0A_LyzM_IYF9zV7WxwfICJOC53yBOj7LcHjVM8vNqA/edit#gid=0" target="_blank"><u
