DESCRIPTION:Hi advocates\,<br><br>Welcome to our joint LegList/Amigos calls
  every Tuesday from 12pm-1pm ET until election week in November.<br><br>Sha
 ring below the *<b>Zoom link</b>* for this call. This is a brand new link s
 pecific to these calls. <br><br><b>Join the Zoom Meeting:</b><br><a href="h
 ttps://theimmigrationhub.zoom.us/j/93022846161" target="_blank"><u>https://
 theimmigrationhub.zoom.us/j/93022846161</u></a><br><br>Meeting ID: 930 2284
  6161<br><br><br>Agenda items are always welcome.<b> Please send <a href="m
 ailto:joshua@theimmigrationhub.org">joshua@theimmigrationhub.org</a> any ag
 enda items by COB on Fridays.</b><br><b><br>Guidelines for the Amigos Lists
 erv &amp\; Calls</b><br>The Amigos network is a collaborative space created
  to facilitate information-sharing and activation of partners on timely imm
 igration issues. We greatly value our partners in the Amigos network and se
 ek to foster a culture of trust\, equity\, and community. With this in mind
 \, we have implemented the guidelines outlined below to inform how we show 
 up for ourselves and for each other. <br><br><b>The full version of the Ami
 gos list guidelines can be found here: </b><a href="https://docs.google.com
 /document/d/1poTzhnjlpqJzdJ65VMkC9Lo091h08Ojj2fpYgkRN9-4/edit?usp=sharing" 
 target="_blank" class="pastedDriveLink-0"><u><u><u>https://docs.google.com/
 document/d/1poTzhnjlpqJzdJ65VMkC9Lo091h08Ojj2fpYgkRN9-4/edit?usp=sharing</u
 ></u></u></a><br><br>Failure to abide by these guidelines may result in rem
 oval from the Hub’s Amigos listserv and may also extend to other Hub listse
 rvs\, such as Leglist and Admin List/Table. Removal from the Amigos calls/l
 istserv can be made at the discretion of Immigration Hub staff and may be d
 one immediately\, without warning\, based on the offending action(s). <br><
 br><b>The Amigos Network</b><br>The purpose of both the Amigos listserv and
  weekly Amigos calls is for organizations to share updates\, resources\, an
 d actions on federal immigration and refugee policy issues\; coordinate adv
 ocacy on federal legislation and executive policy\; and rapidly respond to 
 national immigration and refugee policy developments.<br><br>At this time\,
  approximately 100 partners consistently join the weekly Amigos calls. A re
 gularly-updated list of Amigos partners can be viewed here: <br><br><a href
 ="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Q0A_LyzM_IYF9zV7WxwfICJOC53yBOj7L
 cHjVM8vNqA/edit#gid=0" target="_blank" class="pastedDriveLink-1"><u><u><u>h
 ttps://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Q0A_LyzM_IYF9zV7WxwfICJOC53yBOj7LcHj
 VM8vNqA/edit#gid=0</u></u></u></a><br><br>If you have any questions about t
 he network\, or would like to add people to the listserv\, please email: <a
  href="mailto:Daisy@theimmigrationhub.org">Daisy@theimmigrationhub.org</a>.
  <br><b><u><br></u></b>Best\,<br><br>Josh\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:
 ~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-\nJoin Zoom Meetin
 g\nhttps://theimmigrationhub.zoom.us/j/93022846161 (ID: 93022846161)\n\nJoi
 n by phone\n(US) +1 888-475-4499\n\nJoining instructions: https://www.googl
 e.com/url?q=https://applications.zoom.us/addon/invitation/detail?meetingUui
 d%3Df%252FPWEK1fRwivdAdNgFwqnA%253D%253D%26signature%3D0f628533b788b22cd577
 0fff783b2c9dfe1ea4412e846a8c78fa3f08753b9249%26v%3D1&sa=D&source=calendar&u
 sg=AOvVaw1uYh9CcD7CHunDd1wv7NXv\n\nMeeting host: <a href="mailto:joshua@the
 immigrationhub.org" target="_blank">joshua@theimmigrationhub.org</a><br /><
 br />Join Zoom Meeting: <br /><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https:/
 /theimmigrationhub.zoom.us/j/93022846161&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp
 \;usg=AOvVaw2VtiM1lTGOcb5Aw8jIhr9J" target="_blank">https://theimmigrationh
 ub.zoom.us/j/93022846161</a>\n\nPlease do not edit this section.\n-::~:~::~
