 he meeting will run from <b>10 a.m. ET until 4:30 p.m. ET. </b><u>Lunch wil
 l be provided on site. A virtual option is also available for those unable 
 to attend in person.</u><br><b><br></b><br>This all-day scenario-planning s
 ession will include numerous panels covering potential policy opportunities
  and federal advocacy priorities under a Harris or Trump administration. <u
