DESCRIPTION:Hi advocates\,<br><br>Welcome to our Amigos calls every Tuesday
  from 12pm-1pm ET.<br><br>Sharing below the *<b>Zoom link</b>* for this cal
 l. This is a brand new link specific to these calls. <br><br><b>Join Zoom M
 eeting</b><br><a href="https://theimmigrationhub.zoom.us/j/93071803953?pwd=
 f6bIsNBmpodar3JOMyp72BLXecG0bb.1" target="_blank">https://theimmigrationhub
 .zoom.us/j/93071803953?pwd=f6bIsNBmpodar3JOMyp72BLXecG0bb.1</a><br><br>Meet
 ing ID: 930 7180 3953<br>Password: 124414<br><br>Agenda items are always we
 lcome.<b> Please send <a href="mailto:joshua@theimmigrationhub.org" target=
 "_blank"><u>joshua@theimmigrationhub.org</u></a> any agenda items by COB on
  Fridays.</b><br><b><br>Guidelines for the Amigos Listserv &amp\; Calls</b>
 <br>The Amigos network is a collaborative space created to facilitate infor
 mation-sharing and activation of partners on timely immigration issues. We 
 greatly value our partners in the Amigos network and seek to foster a cultu
 re of trust\, equity\, and community. With this in mind\, we have implement
 ed the guidelines outlined below to inform how we show up for ourselves and
  for each other. <br><br><b>The full version of the Amigos list guidelines 
 can be found here: </b><a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1poTzhnj
 lpqJzdJ65VMkC9Lo091h08Ojj2fpYgkRN9-4/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank"><u><
 u><u><u>https://docs.google.com/document/d/1poTzhnjlpqJzdJ65VMkC9Lo091h08Oj
 j2fpYgkRN9-4/edit?usp=sharing</u></u></u></u></a><br><br>Failure to abide b
 y these guidelines may result in removal from the Hub’s Amigos listserv and
  may also extend to other Hub listservs\, such as Leglist and Admin List/Ta
 ble. Removal from the Amigos calls/listserv can be made at the discretion o
 f Immigration Hub staff and may be done immediately\, without warning\, bas
 ed on the offending action(s). <br><br><b>The Amigos Network</b><br>The pur
 pose of both the Amigos listserv and weekly Amigos calls is for organizatio
 ns to share updates\, resources\, and actions on federal immigration and re
 fugee policy issues\; coordinate advocacy on federal legislation and execut
 ive policy\; and rapidly respond to national immigration and refugee policy
  developments.<br><br>At this time\, approximately 100 partners consistentl
 y join the weekly Amigos calls. A regularly-updated list of Amigos partners
  can be viewed here: <br><br><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/
 d/1Q0A_LyzM_IYF9zV7WxwfICJOC53yBOj7LcHjVM8vNqA/edit#gid=0" target="_blank">
 <u><u><u><u>https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Q0A_LyzM_IYF9zV7WxwfICJ
 OC53yBOj7LcHjVM8vNqA/edit#gid=0</u></u></u></u></a><br><br>If you have any 
 questions about the network\, or would like to add people to the listserv\,
  please email: <a href="mailto:joshua@theimmigrationhub.org" target="_blank
 "><u>joshua@theimmigrationhub.org</u></a><br><b><u><br></u></b>Best\,<br><b
 r>Josh\n\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~
 :~:~:~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-\nJoin Zoom Meeting\nhttps://theimmigrationhub.zoom.u
 s/j/93071803953?pwd=f6bIsNBmpodar3JOMyp72BLXecG0bb.1 (ID: 93071803953\, pas
 scode: 124414)\n\nJoin by phone\n(US) +1 312-626-6799 (passcode: 124414)\n\
 nJoining instructions: https://www.google.com/url?q=https://applications.zo
 om.us/addon/invitation/detail?meetingUuid%3DuH8FAPArQUa%252BsPCkdUKkUg%253D
 %253D%26signature%3Da7d0cb8acf91c51585f489c3c5514ca8579168510dce12e1f9280f0
